asset.hookText:
DC50 is our smallest upright vacuum cleaner with concentrated technology.  Dyson engineers were challenged to develop a small, efficient, powerful machine that performed like a full-size upright. 100 Dyson engineers carefully considered each component over three years; questioning its size, necessity and efficiency.  The technology inside has not simply been 'shrunk', but concentrated. Engineers miniaturised each component, questioning materials as well as size, and efficiency. DC50 has our most advanced cleaner head technology, 2 Tier Radial™ cyclones and the latest Ball™ technology.
